  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9eb0f731-6fd2-439c-b833-bc660719d5ec\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a46121a4-031d-4448-95bc-501e79285453\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bc662ef3-cf55-4f1e-b62d-57d6f846a89d\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 37</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3deda534-2abc-43f7-ac4c-37083efd03da\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1e9a281e-d60e-4410-9b97-4206e9804d52\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6958cca2-a52e-4898-8f40-405ca7910773\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-863ef788-6138-4116-8f16-9f512f829451\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-236606bd-f922-4886-a494-468034920f87\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4ee60b0f-e092-4018-8bb1-cd0e3408577f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-22d372b9-c68f-4ecb-9237-0ea65746ff5a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fbc035b9-72a7-47e9-9ff1-b0618f5a4e96\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6e7f290-b28f-466e-b16e-d35fb3acea47\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee05d4b0-182e-46bd-b251-0f5ca4bcaabd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-dcecb911-d5a4-409e-951f-9bb2ee99a4d7\" style=\"\">성공이라는 못을 박으려면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70b6fc0d-724a-4f80-baec-f7dca998431b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-6f986b91-7999-436a-b540-5edadb2aae16\" style=\"\">끈질김이라는 망치가 필요하다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-791d1d50-2ec8-4698-98b1-7d8b5e6462c2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-281542f4-8828-4d67-9867-f217b8d811c7\" style=\"\">존 메이슨</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-8b6bc3f7-656d-45ec-9fe4-b8ecacd43639\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65f807a8-ea8b-4e73-a2d1-0a032cddaaf4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-192c8bf4-5966-4c95-9c96-5734b31c2118\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>기초데이터 등록</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f75bf543-80a6-4a77-96b5-4605cb42de1a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd6b1f69-5e9b-4d03-8987-c8fe7c3203a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dba806fd-4991-434d-8a0b-0265354ab08b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이번주 내내 엑셀과 기초데이터 작업으로 인해 블로그 업로드를 많이 못했습니다. 죄송합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-00f00f2d-e83e-491f-ae30-03c618bbfb55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c25b5ec-ba54-496e-94ad-0bdc69bc0473\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09273d3f-11e5-405f-876e-2c9f8cbfe7be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-44759b46-f1f8-4914-bcd7-2576a8c38fa4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적으로 사이트나 전화, 메일로 들어 온 인쇄주문을 여러분은 어떻게 관리하고 계신가요? 대부분은 간단한 관리용 프로그램을 구매했거나 아니면 간단하게 자신의 엑셀을 만들어서 활용하는것이 대부분일 겁니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 사이트 개발과 더불어 내부 관리자페이지 개발의 일환으로 인쇄관리용 프로그램을 엑셀과 VBA를 활용하여 개발중입니다. 추후 사이트런칭시에는 내부 인트라넷에 붙여서 활용하고 관리자페이지를 기획하도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9291e8ab-284d-418d-8c47-454f2aad61e0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-70af0002-59c7-4ace-b938-71aa111aa9bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9f960b46-0ea5-4521-bcca-890e33afc7ae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-669b4dc3-6b9c-49d3-95cd-83c3e35f77d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5f73b98-67b8-4a88-b5ca-fb46f7374224\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6bbb4598-c8fc-4c52-8480-9c4f8bbaa2e1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 엑셀은 100% 자사 관리자페이지 개발과 인쇄관리용 프로그램으로 활용되기 위해 기획되었습니다. 다른 일반 쇼핑몰이나 기타 영역에서는 맞지 않을 수 있습니다. 오로지 인쇄회사가 자신의 주문을 조금 더 적극적으로 관리하고 편리하게 사용하기 위해 만들었으며 사이트가 없는 일반 소상공인 인쇄회사들이 활용할 수 있도록 개발되었다는 점을 미리 말씀드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4076c9e8-9941-4e42-9142-76007e00052d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f0d4dd4e-722a-488f-85ea-9ace6f4e558f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5fb584af-d1b0-4219-b674-b66c1bee5d8f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-05d18033-d712-4a1c-93a3-bafd08c78b20\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">진행되는 프로세스는 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5cd1f62-3f4f-4f20-9c19-341028624292\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e04e36ea-0bb0-40ec-ad22-8ac6d8eb1e9c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7547b1ee-c772-4dc8-bbc7-e6d605b8ab0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2f9f5d6-a021-4d0d-9d5e-b27972df35cc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2becfa26-f12c-4b66-b5bf-5310006d34b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5ffe9744-aaec-49b1-83fe-e43f3b41a62c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>       주문접수단계   </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c5b8fd08-8810-4591-abd1-e3c3bcc73b5f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">사이트든 전화나 이메일이든 고객이 주문을 요청하는 경우 1차로 주문에 대한 간단한 사항을 입력합니다.  여기에서는 자동으로 주문ID가 부여되고 제일 기본적인 인쇄물제목과 품목 거래처만을 1차로 적어서 기록할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0b0832c4-e8bf-493c-90bc-e7e7185bcbe6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5ff5f8d1-3b90-44dc-a013-33958611893e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49976f28-fb99-44e2-ae4a-144becb34cef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0b3f6e93-1bb2-459c-904d-10e1fc70107c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-11d3bd62-4729-48d1-9574-2eda60a52d2d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f24466ed-dbfa-4d1b-9de3-3a9e53d86617\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42b28d38-7744-49b1-a5f9-8aed8a770fc9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-95e4e5c7-44b2-4aa8-bb56-252c9e2d6acf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적으로 이런 프로세스를 타고 진행하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-829b4a6c-6c15-42f2-b875-910a29b10040\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a2acfb55-cecd-4d7f-a5ff-7b84d988f6f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1ce76e0-ee80-4afb-87cb-aeaba83cca52\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-100e4b81-aa5f-4816-acee-59d51b39cd6f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-07fb49d5-a7bf-4e1b-a099-2bc3461aab18\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd28d3fe-12c4-4a75-a229-d38ab209117c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ca10184e-c002-44da-8254-86578a748bcc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>견적서 제출단계   </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-da8ff189-b23a-4420-907e-0e884d076c23\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">고객의 문의에 의해 들어 온 일단은 가주문은 아직은 수주가 되기 전입니다. 사이트도 템플릿을 선택하고 견적을 요청했을 뿐 정확한 단가는 아직은 확정되지 않은 상태입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-073d0b05-e49e-47ea-abdd-54c3c983037c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:686px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45155fd0-334e-4a1a-8b4e-5248cf53c8a0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ae5444d-05a8-41cd-ab45-75dc3a533032\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-71cb8be4-123c-46be-a24f-91bf4111864c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9e563bc-6b2d-4d9a-9dab-0d51bd06e9e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6cc69085-b0ff-48a9-bfc1-2ed27fbdf991\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이렇게 주문 및 요청에 의해 들어온 내용은 관리자페이지에서 고유번호 ID와 품목등 기본 사양정도가 선 입력이 될 수 있습니다. 하지만 사이트가 아닌 전화상으로 들어 온 주문이라면 관리자가 직접 내용을 입력해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f4d59bf-b464-404a-9ded-53a9ff5b0f71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-95466374-9ec1-4650-b943-8957b0f93695\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a321c116-bb29-4443-a016-19e6e4b60737\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-50203447-7c2c-482b-bc4d-abc8aa2e938f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기초를 입력 후 추후에 수정할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-39856f2f-78bf-45d9-8120-0194119cd84c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c41d5e93-9f6d-4905-9f17-a908f4e4cb77\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f5f1026c-e49c-4d01-b1ac-9237555cd6e4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-193308e0-1127-4323-aeb5-77fadf887d04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45df1bcf-6742-4cba-a2e1-eef31b8255e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9e8e8d15-9c58-4856-b271-1b8a2468ac21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7520d9cc-3d28-48a4-8ce5-f1f1b46f7d0e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1869607d-e568-4a98-b705-b46dd8d20fa4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3fce43a1-35b3-4f24-8411-6581ff333457\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-757bfedd-f0fc-4ba4-af73-506502f0ca64\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ecb2c8c2-2767-4ec5-99c2-d636542499e4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5dfda41e-16f8-4bc3-a4f8-98821dae5cfa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-956b623b-dd75-452f-a816-c33b83c3ec9c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6c836381-f868-449b-a1f2-8348c22a22d4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">소규모 인쇄회사는 엑세이든 ERP든 복잡하고 어려우면 사용하지 않습니다. 제 경험상 그렇습니다. 디테일하게 관리하거나 방대하게 관리하면 정말 좋은 ERP 이겠지만 이 프로그램은 소규모 인쇄회사가 사용하기 좋은 프로그램으로 개발중입니다. 그래서 툴도 엑셀이라는 툴로 잡았고 추후 관리자페이지 개발도 정말로 필요한 요소만을 집중적으로 관리하는것을 목적으로 하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86ceb76a-466f-45ef-b359-36635a324995\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-81fd7312-8aac-42af-80d8-2e288e289724\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-12ab6a9a-1e47-4dd9-afaa-90b002509af6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222926759535/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cf50f87c-c407-409a-bbe0-be65875d35d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56b53357-92ae-4480-9c3d-17f777c51f5d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e2a7efcc-a2bc-426d-b4c4-4a11c59f83fb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>수주여부 확인   </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3a464b88-4282-4f07-84d5-db3d77de69fa\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">견적서를 제출하고 수주가 확정되는 단계입니다. 견적서는 추후 프로그램과 자동연계할 예정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6590e11b-7421-4473-8064-33efe98686df\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fi